  characterNames:
  - Jonathan Harker
  - Victor Frankenstein
  - Dr. Jekyll & Mr. Hyde
  - Dorian Gray
  characterDiscription:
  - Jonathan Harker is a young man who due to one unfortunate event fell into the
    web of the vile count Dracula. After just barely escaping the castle, he teamed
    up with the illustrious  Van Helsing. But, he lost. Van Helsing is dead, his
    fiance Mina has been turned into a vampire and he is slowly turning into one
    himself. He must slay the count in order to reverse the vampiric affliction of
    him and his beloved.
  - Victor Frankenstein is a true prodigy, creating several new breakthroughs in
    medicine before even getting his doctorate. But now due to his hubris, he is
    but a shell of a man. Everyone he has ever loved is dead, at the hands of his
    creation. And worst yet, it stole his research and has been able to make more
    like it. Now Victor must kill Dracula in order to escape England to track his
    mistake and deal with it once and for all.
  - Dr. Henry Jekyll the respected man of medicine and the notorious Edward Hyde,
    prolific serial killer. They might not seem alike in any regard but they are
    two sides of the same coin, the same man. After a confrontation between the two
    and the formation of an uneasy alliance, they now set out to destroy the Count.
    Jekyll in the name of justice and atonement, and Hyde in the name of freedom.
  - Lord Dorian Gray is an enviable man to say the least. He has money, looks and
    most importantly youth on his side. But in secret, he is an immortal sorcerer
    who sealed his soul into a portrait of himself to age in his stead. His former
    lover Dracula has stolen this most valuable of treasures from him, and now he
    quests to retrieve it.
